<D>__{customer #1 no, give me my damn money back. right now, and i don't have no damn receipt neither. day day okay, sir...but where's the cover? customer #1 i don't have no damn cover.}
<A>__{craig walks in with the notice in hand.}
<D>__{day day i can't give you your damn money back on this. customer #1 bullshit! i will go postal in this mothafucka! day day well, you gonna have to go postal then.}
